body_html:
3 ways to correct this error (of course, only do one of them).

  1. You can add a labels file in assets called labels.txt with the content of labels_mobilenet_quant_v1_224.txt
  2. OR rename the given file in assets called labels_mobilenet_quant_v1_224.txt to labels.txt
  3. OR change the returned value in getLabelPath() in ImageClassifierQuantizedMobileNet.java to return "labels_mobilenet_quant_v1_224.txt";

body:
3 ways to correct this error (of course, only do one of them).

1. You can add a labels file in assets called labels.txt with the content of labels_mobilenet_quant_v1_224.txt
2. OR rename the given file in assets called labels_mobilenet_quant_v1_224.txt to labels.txt
3. OR change the returned value in `getLabelPath()` in ImageClassifierQuantizedMobileNet.java to `return "labels_mobilenet_quant_v1_224.txt";`
